INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('177','5','1268743562','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/pas/1646376685.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/pas/1646376685.html','Professional Pet Sitting and Dog Walking  (Williamstown, North Adams, Lanesboro )','<p><center><b><big><font color=\"blue\">Protect Your Pets and Home--Choose an Insured, Professional Pet Sitter</center></b></big></p></font>\n\n<p><b>BERKSHIRE BARKS PROFESSIONAL PET SERVICE</b> - serving the Adams, North Adams, Williamstown, Lanesboro and Pownal, VT areas.<br><p>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.berkshirebarks.com/\"  rel=\"nofollow\"><big><b><font color=\"blue\">Berkshire Barks Pet Sitting and Dog Walking</a></font></big></b><p> \nA full time professional pet sitting and dog walking business.  Berkshire Barks Pet Sitting and Dog Walking is fully insured, bonded and licensed.  Together we will establish a schedule of care appropriate for your pets.  Berkshire Barks Pet Sitting and Dog Walking strives to provide exceptional care for your pets and give you peace of mind knowing your pets are being cared for by a professional pet care provider. A responsible alternative to boarding kennels or the kid next door.\n\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Complimentary Initial Consultation</li>\n    <li>Mid-Day Walks for Dogs</li>                    \n    <li>In-Your-Home Overnight Pet Sitting</li>\n    <li>Custom Visits for Puppies, Senior Pets and Cats</li>                     \n    <li>Feeding Based on Each Pets Schedule</li>\n    <li>Registered Dietitian (RD) Trained in Animal Nutrition</li>\n    <li>Certified in Pet CPR and First Aid through American Red        Cross</li>        \n    <li>Professionally Insured, Bonded, Licensed</li>\n    <li>Member Pet Sitters International (PSI) and National Association      of       Professional Pet Sitters (NAPPS)</li>\n    <li>References always provided</li><p>\n\n<p><b>Berkshire Barks Pet Service</b> is the most reliable and trustworthy pet service we have ever used. We never worry while away and our dogs are always happy and healthy when we return.  They love having Ellen come to stay with them.....a sure sign that they enjoy being with her. She always follows all of our instructions, gives the dogs great care and exercise and gives us great ideas too!!  Thanks Ellen....we love using <b>Berkshire Barks Pet Service</b>!<br>\n<i>-Brenda and Peter B., Williamstown, MA</i><br><p>\n\n<p>Ellen, who owns <b>Berkshire Barks Pet Service</b>, interacts with dogs in such a way that they seem to know they are special.  It is very rare to know someone like Ellen that you can trust with your dog. Ellen spends quality time with Webster and he loves her and is always excited to see her.  I only have to mention her name and he gets very excited knowing he is going to go for a walk with her.<br>\n<i>-Mariam R., Williamstown, MA</i><br><p>\n\n<p>Please visit <a href=\"http://www.berkshirebarks.com/\"  rel=\"nofollow\"><font color=\"blue\"><b></big>www.berkshirebarks.com</a></font></b></big> to read other testimonials by satisfied pet owners.<br>\n\n\n<p>Contact Ellen to set up your complimentary CONSULTATION.<br>\nellen@berkshirebarks.com<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.berkshirebarks.com/\"  rel=\"nofollow\"><font color=\"blue\"><b></big>www.berkshirebarks.com</a></font></b></big><br>\n413-663-0594<br>	');
