INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('177','7','1268148175','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/biz/1635689685.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/biz/1635689685.html','Birthday Parties MA,Family www.themicrophonezone.com','Birthday Parties MA,Family and Children\'s Activities MA,Family Things To Do MA,children of all ages - Kids Parties MA - Rock Star Party Experience \n<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.themicrophonezone.com/\"  rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.themicrophonezone.com/</a> \n<br>\nLet us make you a rock star! \n<br>\n\n<br>\nThe Rock Star Party introduces our excellent range of parties for children and adults alike. \n<br>\n\n<br>\n4 to 10 singers can participate, age 7 and up! \n<br>\n\n<br>\nNo Experience Necessary! \n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\nFor People Who Love to Sing \n<br>\nChoose your songs to sing from our extensive library of over 95,000 Karaoke backing tracks. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nLet the Microphone Zone take your next party or gathering, from 4 to 10 people, to another exciting level of fun and excitement. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nChildren and adults alike will have a tremendous time and everyone will leave with a memorable CD Keepsake that will last beyond a lifetime. \n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\nThe Microphone Zone Recording Studio \n<br>\nAt the Microphone Zone Professional Recording Studio, we only use the finest state of the art recording equipment. Featuring the finest AKG C414XL Microphones, Sony Headphone, Paris Recording Equipment, Professional Mixing Consoles, as well as state-of-the-art Sony Video Equipment and Monitors. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nHow It Works \n<br>\nUpon booking your experience, we will furnish you with your very own Rock Star Party invitations that you can mail out to all the participants of your party. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nChoose a song~~ \n<br>\nOnce you have decided who\'s in the group and asked them to the party using the supplied invitations, you need to choose the song to be sung from our backing track library. Upon arriving to the Microphone Zone, you will be greeted by our Producer/Engineer, who will assist you in picking your song (or songs) you will be recording, as well as give everyone a complete tour of the studio. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nEveryone will be able to read the lyrics from our Digital LCD Monitor and be prompted when the lyrics need to be sung. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nRehearsing before your recording session~~ \n<br>\nTo get the best from a Rock Star Party, we recommend a group rehearsal prior to your studio session. If the group is confident enough to do solo parts, then clearly mark who-is-doing-what on your lyrics sheets as the producer may ask for a copy. There is enough time to sort out solo parts during the session if none have been predetermined. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nThe recording studio experience day~~ \n<br>\nOn arrival, and before commencing with the recording session, a few pictures of the entire group in their best Rock Star poses are taken. You will also be asked to choose a name for your group. \"Girls Alike\" or \"Street Kids\" are examples of some of the most recent chosen by over 100 parties we\'ve held in our studio. This together with the best picture will create your Souvenir Picture CD, which is given to every singing participant at the end of the session. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nThe real takes~~ \n<br>\nAfter a short break for refreshments, it\'s back to the live room for three real takes. The best bits from all three takes are then compiled together by the producer to from one perfect track ready to be \"burned\" onto your Souvenir Picture CD for taking home at the end of your session. \n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\nGroup or Individual Rock Star Experience \n<br>\nYou will have a choice of either singing together as a group or each person singing individually on their own CD Single (song). \n<br>\n\n<br>\nWhen choosing to sing as a group, 2 to 4 songs can be recorded on your CD, and this will vary with the age and experience level of the singing participants. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nPlease note: The greater the experience level, the more songs can be recorded. If the participants need more time, or are making mistakes requiring the songs to be done over again, then it only makes sense that fewer songs can be recorded in the allotted time frame. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nWhen choosing the Rock Star Party Package, all singing participants can record their own individual song. \n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\nNaming the Individual CDs \n<br>\nYou can choose either a group name or list the singers individually on your souvenir CD. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nDigital Photos \n<br>\nDigital photos will be taken of your group or party prior to the recording experience for the artwork on your souvenir CDs. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nMake Us the \"Event\" Part of Your Party \n<br>\nMake the Microphone Zone Rock Star Party the \"event part\" of your celebration. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nWe recommend that you have your cake and gift-giving part of your party at your home, restaurant, or other venue either prior to or after your Rock Star Party. \n<br>\n\n<br>\nBring everyone down to The Microphone Zone for the \"event part\" of your party, either prior to or after the celebration part for fun and singing excitement! Everyone will leave with a CD with their song(s) and picture(s) on it! \n<br>\n\n<br>\nCall us at \n<br>\n1-978-921-0739 \n<br>\nfor more details about your studio experience, plus new and \n<br>\nused gear. \n<br>\nOr stop by for a visit! --------------------------Abington\n<br>\nActon\n<br>\nAdams\n<br>\nAgawam\n<br>\nAllston\n<br>\nAmesbury\n<br>\nAmherst\n<br>\nAndover\n<br>\nArlington\n<br>\nAshland\n<br>\nAthol\n<br>\nAttleboro\n<br>\nAuburn\n<br>\nAvon\n<br>\nAyer\n<br>\nBedford\n<br>\nBelchertown\n<br>\nBellingham\n<br>\nBelmont\n<br>\nBeverly\n<br>\nBillerica\n<br>\nBoston\n<br>\nBraintree\n<br>\nBrewster\n<br>\nBridgewater\n<br>\nBrighton\n<br>\nBrockton\n<br>\nBrookline\n<br>\nBurlington\n<br>\nBuzzards Bay\n<br>\nCambridge\n<br>\nCanton\n<br>\nCarver\n<br>\nCenterville\n<br>\nCharlestown\n<br>\