INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('178','85','1270140653','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/pet/1671730502.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/pet/1671730502.html','Big City Kitty needs a new home (Williamstown)','Silas came to us through our daughter in NYC where she rescued him. He needed larger space then a small apartment so  we took him in. Before coming to us, he never saw another cat or dog. He gets along fine with our two 1 1/2 year old  Labs no problem but my two- 15 year old female cats he is fighting with and chases them all the time. That\'s why  have to find a new home for him. Right now he is an indoor cat but really wants to be outdoors. He\'s black and white with big yellow eyes and  he is a big boy! He would do best, I think, in a home without other cats and probably not children. He\'s not a cuddler but I think he would be if he weren\'t competing with other animals. ');
