INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('180','94','1270246487','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/vac/1673841776.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/vac/1673841776.html','Stunning 1890\'s Farm (Stephentown, NY) $2500 3bd','This stunning 3 bedroom 2 bath 1890\'s farmhouse is located on the New York/Mass border between Stephentown, NY and Hancock MA.  The home features a state of the art kitches, wood stove, fireplace, two ponds covering 38 bucolic acres.  The Kinderhook Creek, a NY State stocked trout stream also runs along side the property.  The house is available form April 01 through September 01.  One month security deposit is required as are refrences.  We are located 5 minutes from Jiminy Peak, 25 minutes from Williamstown, MA as well as 25 minutes to Lenox MA, the summor home of the Boston Symphony and Tanglewood.');
INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('180','95','1270228996','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/apa/1673339790.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/apa/1673339790.html','Cute 19th century house with gardends (Williamstown) $1300 3bd','Wonderful historic house, located within walking distance of Williams College and downtown.  Located on a large, beautiful, private yard, with a raised-bed garden, magnificent 200 year old oak tree, many lilac trees, flowers, and a great meadow next-door.  Property is near the Hoosic River and just up the street from a very popular local diner.  The house used to belong to the town veterinarian, so there is ample parking and storage available.  Three bedrooms upstairs, with one bathroom, and a very large kitchen, dining room, and living room with working fireplace downstairs.  Hardwood floors throughout and a large basement for more storage.  Washer/dryer hook-ups too.  One bay of a two-bay garage included.  Landlords live right across the street in a historic bed & breakfast.  Rent is $1300 a month, plus utilities (heat, water, electricity).  Heat is oil base-board force water.  Updated thermal windows throughout the home.');
INSERT INTO `feeds_data_classifieds_import` VALUES ('180','96','1270226646','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/vac/1673264782.html','http://westernmass.craigslist.org/vac/1673264782.html','Luxurious House 2 Miles from Jiminy Peak (Hancock, MA) $175 3bd','Come and enjoy our beautiful mountain retreat - A home for every season. This charming home away from home is a wonderful place for family, friends and romance and is located 2 miles from Jiminy Peak and 25 minutes from Lenox and Tanglewood!\n<br>\n\n<br>\nWith over 2200 square feet, this new country home has plenty of space for everyone yet a very cozy feel. Each one of the 3 large bedrooms has walk-in closets and beautiful new funishings. The master suite has a king size bed and matching furniture with a brand-new 32\" Samsung LCD HDTV. The attached master bathroom has a huge Jacuzzi tub for two. Step out onto the balcony from the living room for a magnificent open view of the mountains. Enjoy a movie on your 46\" Sony HDTV while enjoying the heat from the wood-burning stove. The enclosed basement can be used as a playroom or den or as a closed-off 4th bedroom with a couch that opens up into a queen sized bed. Explore the 16 acres of trails on the property and hike your way to the golf course in the back. If you have kids, there are swings and slides on the property for their enjoyment. There\'s also an attached 2 car garage with automatic garage door openers.<br>\n\n<br>\nAnd don\'t forget that just 2 miles down the road is Jiminy Peak - offering skiing and snowboarding day and night. Or drive ten minutes down the road to the Clark Museum in Williamstown and enjoy some Monet and Renoir. Or fifteen minutes down the other direction to the city of Pittsfield for some wonderful restaurants and shops. And don\'t forget that we are only 2 hours and 45 minutes from NYC.\n<br>\n\n<br>\nRates from $150-275/night. $1000/week for the month of April.  Email for availability and last minute specials and check us out at www.vrbo.com/274704 for more pictures and information\n<br>\n\n<br>\n.');
